rn European languages. This was the name of the mother of John the Baptist (Luke 1:60). Etymologically, the name means ‘God is my oath’, and is therefore identical with <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Maitland was born in 1194, in Banffshire, Scotland, United Kingdom as the daughter of Robert Maitland. She had at least 1 son with John Gurdon. She died in 1217, in Dedham, Essex, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 23."},"et":{"1194–1217":"1194–1217","1194–1251":"1194–1251","1217–1287":"1217–1287","1173–1194":"1173–1194","1217":"1217","1287":"1287","1251":"1251","1173":"1173","1194":"1194","Banffshire, Scotland":"Banffshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Dedham, Essex, England":"Dedham, Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1194–1217":"1194–1217","1194–1251":"1194–1251","1217–1287":"1217–1287","1173–1194":"1173–1194","1217":"1217","1287":"1287","1251":"1251","1173":"1173","1194":"1194","Banffshire, Scotland":"Banffshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Dedham, Essex, England":"Dedham, Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1194–1217":"1194–1217","1194–1251":"1194–1251","1217–1287":"1217–1287","1173–1194":"1173–1194","1217":"1217","1287":"1287","1251":"1251","1173":"1173","1194":"1194","Banffshire, Scotland":"Banffshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Dedham, Essex, England":"Dedham, Essex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Maitland est née en 1194, à Banffshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni, fille de Robert Maitland. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec John Gurdon. Elle est décédée en 1217, à Dedham, Essex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 23 ans."},"de":{"1194–1217":"1194–1217","1194–1251":"1194–1251","1217–1287":"1217–1287","1173–1194":"1173–1194","1217":"1217","1287":"1287","1251":"1251","1173":"1173","1194":"1194","Banffshire, Scotland":"Banffshire, Schottland, U